Class XMLParser

java.lang.Object
implementations.XMLParser
public class XMLParser extends Object
XMLParser.java This class parses XML files and validates their structure using custom data structures. It uses MyStack to track opening tags and ensure proper nesting, and MyQueue to store and report errors found during parsing.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Christopher Hanlon, Mikael Ly
